               <msContents>
                  <summary/>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <title>fol. 1r-6v Image of Peter and Paul Chaîne Repertoire number 187</title>
                     
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምክሙ፡ ዘአልባስጥሮስ፡ አፈው።</incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <title>fol. 7r-163r Egzi'abḥer nagśa</title>
                     
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ሥሉስ፡ ዘኢይትዌለጥ፡ በእድ፡ እንተ፡ ኢታስተርኢ፡ ነፍሰ፡ እጓለ፡ እመሕያው፡ ዘይመስጥ። ወአመ፡ ትንሣኤ፡ ሙታን፡ ካዕበ፡ ኀበ፡ ማኅፈደ፡ ሥጋ፡ ዘይሰውጥ።</incipit>
                     <note>Arranged for the months of the year</note>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
