                  <additions><list><item xml:id="e1">Copied by ተክለ፡ ሃይማኖት, fol. 1r-6v. Copied by ተክለ፡ ማርያም፡ ዕፀ፡ ገነት, fol. 7r-163r. Colophon with date, fol. 163rv. Stamps of Trinity Cathedral, ff. 1a, 7a and 163b, and Mal'aka Berhān Takla Wald, ff. 156a and 163ab.</item></list></additions>
                  
                  
